definitions: something that raises levels of physiological or nervous activity in the body or any biological system

examples.text: glucose is the main stimulator of insulin release
nerve stimulators provide soothing therapy for muscle fatigue

shortDefinitions: something that raises levels of physiological or nervous activity in body

definitions: a person or thing that encourages the development of or increased activity in a state or process

examples.text: music is one of the most powerful stimulators of happiness

shortDefinitions: person or thing that encourages increased activity in state or process
